Package: evalfinutTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Process and Analyze Dietary Intake Data from Evalfinut
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jairo H Migueles [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jairo H Migueles <jairo@jhmigueles.com>
Description: Provides tools for reading and processing dietary intake data exported from Evalfinut.
  Includes functions for formatting summary-by-person reports, importing detailed food intake data,
  classifying foods by NOVA processing categories, and calculating energy intake per meal and
  processing level. Designed for use in nutritional epidemiology and dietary pattern research.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
